high_descs: Turn around and walk to the side of the wooden coffee table to the left.
Pick up the watch in front of the laptop computer on the table.
Turn right and walk to the red couch.
Put the watch inside the cardboard box on the right side of the couch.

Turn left, hang a left at the red chair and turn around to face the red chair.
Put the box with the watch inside on the chair.
